6 AS INTRODUCED
6
7 An Act relating to higher education; amending 70 O.S.
7 2021, Section 2632, as amended by Section 1, Chapter
8 129, O.S.L. 2025 (70 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 2632),
8 which relates to eligibility for an Oklahoma Tuition
